      <div class="faq-item grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
        <div class="md:col-span-4"><h4 class="display-md text-lg">Are you vendor-approved with major agencies?</h4></div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 text-[15px] leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--cream-dim);">
          We're onboarded as a preferred vendor with several national agency networks and CPG brand teams. References available on request.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
